@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Nhân viên" as Staff
participant "IncidentPanel\n(View)" as View
participant "IncidentController" as Controller
participant "IncidentService" as Service
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over Staff, DB: QUY TRÌNH GHI NHẬN VÀ CẬP NHẬT SỰ CỐ

Staff -> View : 1. Nhập nội dung sự cố & phòng
View -> Controller : 2. reportIncident(roomId, content)
activate Controller

Controller -> Service : 3. saveIncident(roomId, content, currentStaffId)
activate Service

Service -> DB : 4. INSERT INTO PHAN_HOI (trang_thai = 'CHO_XU_LY')
activate DB
DB -->> Service : 5. Success
deactivate DB

Service -->> Controller : 6. Incident Reported
deactivate Service
Controller -->> View : 7. Hiển thị: "Đã báo Admin"

Note over Staff, DB: Sau khi thợ sửa xong

Staff -> View : 8. Bấm nút "Xác nhận hoàn thành"
View -> Controller : 9. resolveIncident(incidentId)
activate Controller
Controller -> Service : 10. updateIncidentStatus(incidentId, 'HOAN_THANH')
activate Service
Service -> DB : 11. UPDATE PHAN_HOI SET trang_thai = 'HOAN_THANH'
DB -->> Service : 12. Success
Service -->> Controller : 13. Resolved
deactivate Service
Controller -->> View : 14. Hiển thị trạng thái mới
deactivate Controller
@enduml